    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "四朝臣",
        "大太监甲",
        "我手中有兵刃定决一死战",
        "秦王",
        "赵艳容",
        "赵高"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖西皮小开门〗。四小太监、二大太监、秦王同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "凤阁龙楼，万古千秋。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四朝臣同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四朝臣",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣等见驾，吾皇万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众卿平身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四朝臣",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵高上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣赵高见驾，吾皇万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "平身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卿女可曾带上金殿？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣启万岁：臣女昨晚偶得疯癫之症，请主定夺。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "昨晚灯光之下还是好人，怎么得了疯症？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有道是：天有不测风云，人有旦夕祸福。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赐她龙车凤辇，带上金殿，寡人观看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵高下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "御林军走上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "御林军进殿哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四御林军同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "殿角侍候。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵高、哑奴、赵艳容同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "低着头下了这龙车凤辇，\n行一步来至在玉石阶前。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵艳容示意哑奴在殿外等侯，哑奴下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "到如今顾不得抛头露面，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿啊，随我上殿。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵艳容冷笑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，坏了，坏了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "且看这无道君怎把旨传。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿啊，上面就是万岁，上前见驾。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我晓得。\n哟，上面坐的敢莫是皇帝老官么？恭喜你万福，贺喜你发财呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗯！见了寡人因何不跪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有道是，这大人不下位，我生员么，喏喏喏，是不跪的哟！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果然疯癫，倒叫寡人好笑哇，哈哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我也好笑哇，哈哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗯！寡人笑你疯癫，你笑寡人何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你笑得我疯癫，我就笑得你这荒淫无道！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎见得寡人无道？"
        },
        {
          "character": "四朝臣",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾主乃有道明君。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "列位大人，老哥，你等听了！想先皇当年，东封泰岱，西建咸阳，南修五岭，\n北造万里长城；指望江山万代，永保平安，不想你这昏王荒淫无道，不理朝纲。\n我想这天下乃人人之天下，非你一人之天下，似你这样宠信奸佞，沉迷酒色；\n这江山，你家未必坐得长久哟！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "这昏王失仁义民心大变，\n听谗言害忠良败坏了江山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "真乃疯话，哪里容得。\n左右，刀门架起！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唗！我把你们这些狐假虎威的强盗，狗仗人势的奴才！我乃丞相之女，指挥老\n爷之妻，岂容你们这等放肆，大胆！哎呀，要记……记责啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "怒冲冲我把这云鬟扯乱，\n气得我咬牙关火上眉尖。\n将这些众狂徒就斩首在马前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "我手中有兵刃定决一死战、秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再若疯癫，斩头来见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦哟哟，我也不知道这皇帝老官有多大的脸面，动不动就要斩头来见。你要晓\n得，一个人的头斩了下来，是还能长得上的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳，一个人的头斩了下来，是长不上了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，长不上了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "长不上了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉，爹爹！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "哭头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊……老爹爹，我的儿啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，又来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "这一番在金殿装疯弄险，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赶下殿去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（哑奴迎上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵艳容",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "但不知何日里夫妻重圆。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（三笑） 哈哈，哈哈，啊哈哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（哑奴扶赵艳容同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老臣领罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罚俸三月。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢主龙恩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "退班！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人自两边分下。）"
        }
      ],
